			<div class="item-page">
	<h2>
			<a href="/index.php/en/128-amendment-of-the-september-26-2012-meeting-minutes">
		Amendment of the September 26, 2012 meeting minutes</a>
		</h2>

	<ul class="actions">
			<li>
		<a href="#" onclick="window.print();return false;"><img src="/media/system/images/printButton.png" alt="Print"  /></a>		</li>
	
	</ul>






	<div>Unfortunately, GSS head office did not liked the wording that we used in our meeting minutes from the September 26th.</div>
<div> </div>
<div>Because of that some of our colleagues have troubles with reimbursements for the things we already purchased and using, namely  HDTV in the game room, ping-pong bats, Fifa 13, and kitchen supplies.</div>
<div> </div>
<div>
<div>Therefore I've amended our meeting minutes in order to make our financial motions  and make sure they comply with the GSS wording requirements.</div>
<div style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Example:</span></div>
<div style="padding-left: 60px;"><strong>Old wording:</strong> </div>
<div style="padding-left: 60px;"><strong><br /></strong></div>
<div style="padding-left: 60px;">Motion to buy HDTV for games room</div>
</div>
<div style="padding-left: 60px;">
<p>                                                            Volunteer: <strong>Majid Razmara</strong></p>
<p>                                                            Moved by: Svetozar Miuchin</p>
<p>                                                            Seconded by: Ravikran Vadlapudi</p>
<p>                                                            Budget: $700</p>
<p>                                                            Vote for: 14</p>
<p>                                          Decision: <strong>Motion carries</strong></p>
</div>
<div style="padding-left: 60px;"> </div>
<div style="padding-left: 60px;"><strong> New wording:</strong></div>
<div style="padding-left: 60px;">
<p><strong> </strong>Motion to buy <span>HDTV</span> for games room and to approve that <strong>Majid Razmara</strong> will spend up to $700 and got reimbursed for this purchase.</p>
<p>                                                            Volunteer: <strong>Majid Razmara</strong></p>
<p>                                                            Moved by: Svetozar Miuchin</p>
<p>                                                            Seconded by: Ravikran Vadlapudi</p>
<p>                                                            Budget: $700</p>
<p>                                                            Vote for: 14</p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div> </div>
<div>As you might see now motion reads who exactly would be able to spend the money and how much.</div>
<div>The amended meeting minutes could be found in our <a href="http://csgsa.cs.sfu.ca/index.php/en/minutes/127-amended-minutes-for-cs-gsa-meeting-on-september-26-2012">meeting minutes section</a></div>
<div> </div>
<div> </div>
<div>Now in order to approve amendments we need to conduct web-survey and received at least 10 votes in favor of approval.</div>
<div>Please, support the amendment of our minutes and vote <a href="http://websurvey.sfu.ca/survey/125542904">using this web-survey</a> </div>
<div> </div>
<div><strong>Update 8/11/2012</strong><span style="color: #ff0000;"> Web-survey is closed now. Thank you everyone for voting.</span></div> <div class="attachmentsContainer">

